        span.d-legened.d-legened-2 aria-live='people-oriented'
          em d 
          |= 2.60
    .feedback.feedback-2.col-12.col-md-10.mt-4.incomplete
      p.mb-0.main-text-2 
        |For this example, slide the two curves to estimate how much men and women prefer people-oriented careers (for example, being a health professional or counselor). Place the one you think is higher on the right. When you’re ready, select “Submit.”
